TECH_PARAM_1.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: statistics on Argos or GPS received data
TECH_PARAM_1.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: total number of Argos positions received.

TECH_PARAM_3.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: positioning (ARGOS message) - Class 1 - accuracy better than 1500m radius

TECH_PARAM_4.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: positioning (ARGOS message) - Class 2 - accuracy better than 500m radius

TECH_PARAM_5.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: positioning (ARGOS message) - Class 3 - accuracy better than 250m radius

TECH_PARAM_13.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: number of valve actions at the surface
TECH_PARAM_13.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of solenoid valve actions at the surface until the crossing of the GAP threshold

TECH_PARAM_14.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: time when first stabilization appears during descent to park (tenths of an hour since midnight)

TECH_PARAM_15.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: number of valve actions in descent
TECH_PARAM_15.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of valve actions between the crossing  of the gap threshold and the end of descent at park pressure

TECH_PARAM_16.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: number of pump actions in descent
TECH_PARAM_16.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of pump actions between the crossing  of the gap threshold and the end of descent at park pressure

TECH_PARAM_17.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: time when park pressure is reached  (tenths of an hour since midnight)

TECH_PARAM_18.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of times the float readjusts its buoyancy during park phase - using either the pump or EV

TECH_PARAM_19.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: time of the first transmission for this cycle

TECH_PARAM_20.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: number of pump actions in ascent
TECH_PARAM_20.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of pump actions between start and end of ascent

TECH_PARAM_21.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Distinct frames emitted on descending profile

TECH_PARAM_22.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: statistics on Argos or Iridium received data
TECH_PARAM_22.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Provor frames received on descending profile

TECH_PARAM_23.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Distinct frames emitted on immersion profile

TECH_PARAM_24.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Distinct frames emitted on ascending profile

TECH_PARAM_25.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: statistics on Argos or Iridium received data

TECH_PARAM_26.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: number of descent slices in shallow zone
TECH_PARAM_26.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Descending profile reduction Number of slices in shallow zone - NTS

TECH_PARAM_27.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: number of descent slices in deep zone
TECH_PARAM_27.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Descending profile reduction Number of slices in deep zone - NTF

TECH_PARAM_28.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: total number of slices of the descending profile after reduction

TECH_PARAM_29.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: statistics on Argos or Iridium received data

TECH_PARAM_30.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: number of ascent slices in shallow zone
TECH_PARAM_30.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Ascending profile reduction Number of slices in shallow zone - NTS

TECH_PARAM_31.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: number of ascent slices in deep zone
TECH_PARAM_31.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Ascending profile reduction Number of slices in deep zone - NTF

TECH_PARAM_32.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: total number of slices of the ascending profile after reduction

TECH_PARAM_33.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: statistics on Argos or Iridium received data

TECH_PARAM_34.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: number of CTD measurements in drift

TECH_PARAM_35.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: statistics on Argos or Iridium received data
TECH_PARAM_35.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Distinct frames received with crc ok on immersion profile

TECH_PARAM_36.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: statistics on Argos or Iridium received data

TECH_PARAM_38.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: Argos or Iridium date of technical message

TECH_PARAM_40.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Surface pressure recorded just before the previous descent but data is corrected on board the float. Note: cumulative NEGATIVE   offset  (real offset * -1) but no further correction required. Autocorrected

TECH_PARAM_42.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: ascent start time (tenths of an hour since midnight)

TECH_PARAM_43.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: number of entrance in drift target range (descent)
TECH_PARAM_43.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: descent to park pressure: number of entries in margin around park pressure target - specifically, how many times the float enters the band of pressure surrounding the target park pressure (generally +/- 30db)

TECH_PARAM_44.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: number of hydraulic valve action in descent profile
TECH_PARAM_44.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of valve actions during descent to start profile pressure

TECH_PARAM_45.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: number of pump actions in descent profile
TECH_PARAM_45.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: number of pump actions during descent to start profile pressure

TECH_PARAM_46.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: number of re-positionning in profile stand-by
TECH_PARAM_46.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: at profile pressure stand-by, number of times the float readjusts its buoyancy - using either the pump or EV

TECH_PARAM_47.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: batteries voltage drop at Pmax, pump ON (with regard to Unom = 10.0 V) (in dV)

TECH_PARAM_48.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: time when descent to profile pressure starts  (tenths of an hour since midnight)

TECH_PARAM_49.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: time when float reaches profile pressure  (tenths of an hour since midnight)

TECH_PARAM_50.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: real time clock status - 1= OK, 0=not OK

TECH_PARAM_51.TECH_PARAM_MSG_LABEL: number of entrance in profile target range (descent)
TECH_PARAM_51.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: descent to profile pressure: number of entries in margin around profile pressure target  - specifically, how many times the float enters the band of pressure surrounding the target profile pressure (generally +/- 30db)

TECH_PARAM_52.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Number of times technical message has been received.

TECH_PARAM_53.TECH_PARAM_DESCRIPTION: Time difference between first and last Argos float messages assigned to the cycle.
